type: web_research
title: LiteLLM Proxy + GPTCache Integration Research (Feb 2026)
source: "https://docs.litellm.ai"
key_insights[10]: "LiteLLM latest version: v1.81.9 (Feb 7, 2026), actively maintained with frequent releases",LiteLLM has NATIVE semantic caching via Redis Semantic Cache and Qdrant Semantic Cache - GPTCache integration is NOT needed,"GPTCache integration was requested (issue #1541) and led to LiteLLM building its own semantic cache (PR #1829, v1.22.10)",LiteLLM supports budget limits at key/user/team/customer/tag/provider levels with auto-reset (daily/weekly/monthly),"Fallback chains support: model-specific, default, content_policy, context_window fallbacks with retry logic",Claude Code can connect to LiteLLM via ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL and ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN env vars,"LiteLLM cost tracking: automatic for 100+ models, dashboard at /ui, API endpoints for spend queries","Docker deployment: litellm + PostgreSQL + Redis, Helm chart available (beta)",Qdrant semantic cache is the recommended alternative to Redis Semantic Cache for local/self-hosted setups,GPTCache project (7.9k stars) supports custom embeddings but has no native LiteLLM integration
findings[7]: LiteLLM's built-in semantic caching eliminates the need for GPTCache,"Redis Semantic Cache requires RediSearch module (redis-stack), Qdrant is simpler for self-hosted",Budget enforcement rejects requests with ExceededTokenBudget error when limits hit,"DualCache architecture: in-memory + Redis for sub-ms lookups with distributed fallback","Cache key includes: model, messages, temperature, top_p, max_tokens, user ID","Per-request cache control: ttl, s-maxage, no-cache, no-store, namespace parameters",Streaming may bypass caching mechanisms - known limitation
recommendations[6]: Use LiteLLM's native Qdrant Semantic Cache instead of GPTCache for simplest integration,"Deploy with Docker Compose: litellm + PostgreSQL + Redis + Qdrant","Set budget_duration: '30d' for monthly spending caps","Use fallback chains: Anthropic -> OpenRouter -> Ollama for cost optimization","Configure similarity_threshold: 0.8 for balanced cache accuracy",Use nomic-embed-text via Ollama as embedding model for Qdrant semantic cache
